\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}5 ounces fresh {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/shiitake/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 shiitake mushrooms}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}5 ounces fresh {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/portobello-mushroom/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 portobello mushrooms}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}5 ounces fresh {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/cremini/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 cremini}} (or {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/porcini/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 porcini}}) mushrooms\
